hadiths[88]{hadithnumber,text}:
4254,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Salim bin-Abdullah se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah Allah Taala tumhen apne baap-dada w ijdaad ki qism khaney se mana karta hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! jab se maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke aap ne us se mana farmaya hai, maine na (apni taraf se) na ( kisi ki) pairwi kartey huey kabhi un ( baap-dada w ijdaad ki) qism khaaii. (baap-dada aur purkhon ki qism ke alfaz hi zaban se ada nahi kiye. ("
4255,"Aqeel-bin-Khalid aur Mamar donon ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta Aqeel ki hadis mein hai : maine jab se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us se mana kartey huey suna, na unki qism khaai aur na aisi qism ke alfaz boley . unhon-ne na apni taraf se na kisi ki pairwi kartey huey ke alfaz nahi kahey ."
4256,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna, wo apne walid ki qism kha rahe they. ( aagey ( Yunus aur Mamar ki riwayat ki tarah hai."
4257,"Leis ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko aik qafley mein paya aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) apne walid ki qism kha rahe they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein pukar kar farmaya : sun rakho ! bila shubah Allah tumhen mana karta hai ke tum apne baap-dada ki qism khaao, jisne qism khaani hai wo Allah ki qism khaaey ya khamosh rahe."
4258,"Abdullah-bin-Numair, Ubaidullah , Ayub , Waleed bin Kasir , Ismail bin Umayya , Suhak , ibne-abi-Ze-ib aur Abdul-Karim , un sab ke shagirdon ne unse aur unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi qissey ki tarah bayan kya."
4259,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne qism khaani hai wo Allah ke siwa kisi ki qism na khaaey aur Quraish apne baap-dada ki qism khaatey they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne baap-dada ki qism na khaao ."
4260,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se jisne Halaf uthaya aur apne Halaf mein kaha : laat ki qism ! to wo la ilaa-h illallaah kahey aur jisne apne sathi se kaha : aao, juwa khelein to wo sadqa kare."
4261,"Auzai aur Mamar donon ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur Mamar ki hadis Yunus ki hadis ki tarah hai, albatta unhon-ne kaha : to wo kuchh sadqa kare. aur Auzai ki hadis mein hai : jisne laat aur uzzaa ki qism khaai. abu-Husain muslim) kitab lekhak ( ne kaha : ye kalima , aap ke farman : (jo kahey ( aao, main tumharey sath juwa khelon to wo sadqa kare. usey imam Zohri ke ilawa aur koi riwayat nahi karta. unhon-ne kaha : aur Zohri (Rehmatullahi-alaih)  ke taqriban nawwey kalimaat ( jumley ( hain jo wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jaiyed sanadon ke sath riwayat kartey hain, jin (ke bayan karne) mein aur koi unka Sharik nahi hai."
4262,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum buton ki qism na khaao , na hi apne baap-dada aur ijdaad ki."
4263,"Ghailan bin Jarir ne abu-Burda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, mein ash-ariyon ki aik jamat ke sath tha. ham aap se sawari ke talabgaar they. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main tumhen sawari muhaiya nahi karunga aur na mere paas (koi sawari) hai jis par main tumhen sawar karun. kaha : jitni der Allah ne chaha ham thehrey, phir (aap ke paas) oont laey gaey to aap ne hamein safaid kohan waley teen (jodey) oont dene ka hukm diya, jab ham chaley, ham ne kaha : ya ham ne aik doosrey se kaha, padhi. Allah hamein barkat nahi dega, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein sawari hasil karne ke liye hazir huey they, to aap ne hamein sawari na dene ki qism khaai, phir aap ne hamein sawari de di, chunanche wo log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye baat kahi to aap ne farmaya : maine tumhen sawar nahi kya, balke Allah ne tumhen sawari muhaiya ki hai aur Allah ki qasam! agar Allah chahey, main kisi cheez par qism nahi khata aur phir (kisi doosrey kaam ko) us se behtar khayal karta hun, to main apni qism ka kaffara deta hun aur wahi kaam karta hun jo behtar hai."
4264,"Buraid ne abu-Barda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere sathiyon ne mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja taake main aap se unke liye sawaariyan maangun, (ye us mauqe ki baat hai) jab wo aap ke sath jaishul-Usra mein they. aur us se murad jange-Tabook hai. to maine kaha : Allah ke Nabi! mere sathiyon ne mujhey aap ke paas bheja hai taake aap unhein sawaariyan din. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main tumhen kisi cheez par Sawar nahi karunga aur main aisey waqt aap ke paas gaya tha ke aap ghussey mein they aur mujhey malum na tha. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke inkar ki wjah se aur us dar se ke aap apne dil mein mujh se naraz ho gaey hain, ghamgeen wapas hua. main apne sathiyon ke paas wapas aaya aur jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha, unhein bataya . maine aik chhoti si ghadi hi guzari hogi ke achcha maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna, wo pukar rahe they : aey Abdullah-bin-Qais! maine unhein jawab diya to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho jao, wo tumhen bula rahe hain. jab main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye 2 ikatthey bandhey huey oont ley lo, ye joda aur ye joda bhi ley lo. padhi. chh oonton ki taraf ishara kya jo aap ne usi waqt Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se khareedey they. aur unhein apne sathiyon ke paas ley jao aur kaho : Allah taalaa, ya farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumhen ye sawaariyaan muhaiya kar rahe hain, un par sawari karo. Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main unhein lekar apne sathiyon ke paas gaya aur kaha : bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumhen un par Sawar kar rahe hain lekin Allah ki qism ! main us waqt tak tumhen nahi chhodunga yahan tak ke tum mein se koi mere sath us aadmi ke paas jaey jisne us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baat suni thi jab maine aap se tumharey liye sawal kya tha, aur pehli martaba aap ke mana karne aur uske baad mujhey ata karne ki baat bhi suni thi, kahin aisa na ho ki tum samjho ki maine tumhen aisi baat batai hai jo aap ne nahi farmai. to unhon-ne mujh se kaha : Allah ki qism ! aap hamarey nazdeek sacchey hain aur jo aapko pasand hai wo bhi ham zaroor karengey, chunanche Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) unmein se chand logon ko sath lekar chal padey yahan tak ke un logon ke paas aaey jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baat aur aap ke inkar karne ke baad ata karne ke barey mein khud suna tha. unhon-ne bilkul wahi baat ki jo Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne (apne) logon ko batai thi."
4265,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba aur Qasim bin Aasim se aur unhon-ne zahdam Jarmi se riwayat ki. padhi. Ayub ne kaha : abu-Qilaba ki hadis ki nisbat mujhey Qasim ki hadis zyada yad hai. unhon ( Zahdam ( ne kaha : ham Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they, unhon-ne apna dasterkhan mangwaya jis par murghi ka gosht tha, itney mein banu-Taimillah mein se aik aadmi andar dakhil hua, wo surkh rang ka mawaali jaisa shakhs tha, to unhon-ne us se kaha : aao. wo hichkichaya to unhon-ne kaha : aao, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us ( murghi ke gosht ( mein se khaatey huey dekha hai. us aadmi ne kaha : maine usey koi aisi cheez khaatey huey dekha tha jis se mujhey us se ghin aai to maine qism khaai thi ke main us (ke gosht) ko kabhi nahi khaaunga. is par unhon-ne kaha : aao, main tumhen iske barey mein hadis sunaata hun, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, main ash-ariyon ke aik garoh ke sath tha, ham aap se sawaariyon ke talabgaar they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qasam! main tumhen sawari muhaiya nahi karunga aur na mere paas koi aisi cheez hai jis par main tumhen sawar karun. jitna Allah ne chaha ham rukey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ( kaafiron se) chheney huey oont (jo aap ne Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se khareed liye they) laey gaey to aap ne hamein bulwaya, aap ne hamein safaid kohan waley panch (ya chh, hadis : 4264) oont dene ka hukm diya. kaha : jab ham chaley, to ham mein se kuchh logon ne dusron se kaha : (ghaaliban) ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apni qism se ghaafil kar diya, hamein barkat na di jaeygi, chunanche ham wapas aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! ham aap ki khidmat mein sawaariyan leney ke liye hazir huey they aur aap ne hamein sawari na dene ki qism khaai thi, phir aap ne hamein sawaariyan de di hain to Allah ke rasool! kya aap bhool gaey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qasam! Allah ki marzi se main jab bhi kisi cheez par qism khata hun, phir iske ilawa kisi aur kaam ko us se behtar khayal karta hun to wahi kaam karta hun jo behtar hai aur (qasam ka kaffara ada karke) uska bandhan khol deta hun. tum jao, tumhen izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne sawar kya hai."
4266,"abdul-wahaab Saqafi ne hamein Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba aur Qasim tamimi se aur unhon-ne Zahdam jurmi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Jaram ke qabeeley aur ash-ariyon ke darmyan mohabbat w ukhuwat ka rishta tha, ham Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they, unhein khana pesh kya gaya jis mein murghi ka gosht tha. padhi. aagey usi ke ham mana bayan kya."
4267,"Ismail bin-Ulaih, Sufiyan aur Wuhaib, sab ne Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba aur Qasim se aur unhon-ne Zahdam jarmi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they. un sab ne Hammad-bin-Zaid ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
4268,"Matar warraaq ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Zahdam Jarmi ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaya, wo murghi ka gosht kha rahe they. unhon-ne un sab ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur is mein ye izafa kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main is (apni qasam) ko nahi bhula."
4269,"Jarir ne hamein Sulaiman Taimi se khabar di, unhon-ne zarb bin naqeer Qaisi se, unhon-ne Zahdam se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein sawaariyaan hasil karne ke liye hazir huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere paas koi cheez nahi hai jis par main tumhen sawar karun Allah ki qism ! main tumhen sawar nahi karunga . phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamari taraf safaid kohan waley teen ( jodey ( oont bhejey to ham ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aap se sawaariyaan hasil karne ke liye hazir huey to aap ne hamein sawari na dene ki qism khaai thi, chunanche ham aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aapko (aap ki qism (ke barey mein) khabar di to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main kisi cheez par qism nahi khaata, phir iske ilawa kisi doosrey kaam ko us se behtar khayal karta hun to wahi karta hun jo behtar ho."
4270,"Motamir ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein abu Saleel (zareeb) ne Zahdam se hadis bayan ki, wo Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne kaha : ham paidal they, to ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, ham aap se sawaariyaan hasil karna chahtey they, ( aagey isi tarah hai) jis tarah Jarir ki hadis hai."
4271,"abu-Hazim ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi raat ki taareeki gehri honey tak Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas raha, phir apne ghar lota to usne bachchon ko soya hua paya, uski biwi uske paas khana laai to usne qism khaai ke wo bachchon (ke so janey) ki wjah se khana nahi khaaeyga, phir usey (doosra) khayal aaya to usne khana kha liya, iske baad wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se is baat ka tazkira kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne koi qism khaai, phir us ne kisi doosrey kaam ko us se behtar samjha to wo wahi kaam kar ley aur apni qism ka kaffara ada kar de."
4272,"Imam Malik ne Suhel bin abi Saleh se khabar di, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne koi qism khaai, phir iske bajaey kisi doosrey kaam ko us se behtar khayal kya to wo apni qism ka kaffara de aur wo kaam kar ley."
4273,"Abdul-Azeez bin Muttalib ne Suhel bin abi Saleh se riwayat ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne koi qism khaai, phir iske bajaey doosrey kaam ko us se behtar khayal kya to wo wahi kaam karey jo behtar hai aur apni qism ka kaffara ada kare."
4274,Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne mujhey Suhel se isi sanad ke sath Imam Malik ki hadis ke ham mana hadis (un alfaz mein) bayan ki : usey chahiye ke apni qism ka kaffara de aur wo kaam karey jo behtar hai.
4275,"Jarir ne Abdul-Azeez bin Raafe se, unhon-ne Tameem bin tarfa se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Adi-bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aik saail aaya aur unse ghulam ki qeemat ya ghulam ki qeemat ka kuchh hissey (ada karne ke liye) kharchey ka sawal kya, to unhon-ne kaha, mere paas to tumhen dene ke liye meri zirah aur) sar ke) khaud ke siwa kuchh nahi, isliye main apne ghar walon ko likh deta hun ke wo ye kharcha tumhen de dein. kaha : wo (us par) razi na hua to Hazrat Adi (Raziallahu anhu) naraz ho gaey aur kaha : Allah ki qism ! main tumhen kuchh nahi doonga , phir wo aadmi (usi baat par) razi ho gaya to unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey na suna hota : jisne koi qism khaai, phir kisi aur kaam ko izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke taqwa ke zyada qareeb dekha to wo taqwa wala kaam kare. to main apni qism na todta."
4276,"Shoba ne Abdul-Azeez bin rafeea' se, unhon-ne Tameem-bin-tarfa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Adi-bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne koi qism khaai, phir kisi doosrey kaam ko us se behtar samjha to wo wahi kaam karey jo behtar hai aur apni qism ko tark kar de. (aur kaffara ada kar de.)"
4277,"Aamash ne Abdul-Azeez-bin-rafeea' se, unhon-ne Tameem Tai se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Adi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi kisi kaam ki qism khaaey , phir us se behtar ( kaam ( dekhey to wo us ( qism (ka kaffara ada kar de aur wahi karey jo behtar hai."
4278,"Shebani ne Abdul-Azeez bin rafeea' se, unhon-ne Tameem Tai se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Adi-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap yahi farma rahe they."
4279,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Samak-bin-Harab se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Tameem-bin-tarfa se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Adi-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unke paas aik aadmi aik so dirham maangney ke liye aaya tha, ( ghulam ki qeemat mein se so dirham kam they) unhon-ne kaha : to mujh se ( sirf ( so dirham maang raha jabke main Hatim Tai ka betaa hun? Allah ki qism ! main tumhen ( kuchh ( nahi doonga , phir unhon-ne kaha : agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey na suna hota : jisne koi qism khaai, phir us se behtar kaam dekha to wo wahi karey jo behtar hai. (to main tumhen kuchh na deta .)"
4280,"Behaz ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis sunai aur kaha : hamein Samak-bin-Harab ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Tameem-bin-tarfa se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Adi-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke aik aadmi ne unse sawal kiya. padhi. aagey usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah bayan kiya aur ye izafa kiya : mere wazeefey mein se char so ( dirham ( tumharey ."
4281,"Sheban-bin-Farukh ne kaha : hamein Jareer-bin-Haazim ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Hasan ne hadis sunai, (kaha : ( hamein Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : Abdur-Rehman bin Samra ! tum ( khud ( amaarat ki darkhaast mat karo, (kyonke) agar wo tumhen maangney par di gaee to tum iske hawale kar diye jaogey aur agar tumhen bin maangey milegi to (Allah ki taraf se) tumhari madad ki jaeygi aur jab tum kisi kaam par qism khaao, phir iske bajaey kisi doosrey kaam ko us se behtar dekho to apni qism ka kaffara do aur wahi ikhtiyar karo jo behtar hai. (Imam Muslim ke shagird ( abu Ahmed juludi ne kaha : hamein abu Abbas Nasarjasi ne hadis sunai, (kaha : ( hamein Sheban-bin-Farukh ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Jareer-bin-Haazim ne isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki."
4282,"Yunus , Mansoor , Humaid , Samak bin Atiya , Hisham bin Hassan , Motamir ke walid ( Sulaiman tarkhaan (aur Qatada , un sab ne Hasan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis bayan ki aur Motamir ki apne walid ( Sulaiman tarkhaan ( se riwayat ki hui hadis mein amaarat ( wali baat (ka zikr nahi."
4283,"Yahya-bin-Yahya aur Amr Naqid ne hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. Yahya ne kaha : hamein Hushaim bin Bashir ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai Saleh se khabar di aur Amr ne kaha : hamein Hushaim bin Bashir ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Ubai Saleh ne khabar di. padhi. unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhari qism isi baat par hogi jis par tumhara sathi (qasam leney wala) tumhari tasdeeq karega aur Amr ne kaha : jiski tasdeeq tumhara sathi karega."
4284,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne Hushaim se, unhon-ne Ibad bin abi Saleh se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qasam, Halaf leney waley ki niyat ke mutabiq hogi."
4285,"Muhammad (bin Sirin ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ki sath beeviyan thin, unhon-ne kaha : (Allah ki qasam) aaj raat mein un sab ke paas jaaunga to unmein se har biwi haamla hogi aur har biwi (eik shehsawaar) bachchey ko janm degi, jo Allah ki raah mein ladai karega. to aik ke siwa unmein se koi haamla na hui aur us ne bhi adhoorey (naaqis paida honewaley) bachchey ko janm diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar wo inshaAllah kehtey to unmein se har biwi shehsawaar bachchey ko janm deti jo Allah ki raah mein ladai karta."
4286,"Hisham bin Hujair ne Taaus se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : Allah ke Nabi Sulaimaan-bin-Daawood (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : ( Allah ki qism ( aaj raat mein 70 aurton ke paas jaunga, wo sab eik-eik bachchey ko janm dengi jo Allah ki raah mein ladai karega. to unse unke kisi sathi ya Farishtey ne kaha : inshaAllah kahin. unhon-ne na kaha, unhein bhula diya gaya, unki aurton mein se aik aurat ke siwa kisi ne bachchey ko janm na diya, usne bhi adhoorey bachchey ko janm diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar wo inshaAllah kehtey to qism tishna takmeel na rehti aur ye ( qism ( unki zarurat (apni aulad ke zariey se jihad fi-sabeelillah) ki takmeel ka sabab bhi bin jati."
4287,"Sufiyan ne abu-Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah ya usi ke ham-mana riwayat bayan ki."
4288,"Taaus ke betey ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Sulaimaan-bin-Daawood (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : aaj raat mein 70 aurton ke paas chakkar lagaaunga, unmein se har aurat ( biwi ya kaneez ( aik bachchey ko janm degi jo Allah ki raah mein ladai karega. to unse kaha gaya : inshaAllah kahiye. unhon-ne na kaha (unhein bhula diya gaya). wo unke paas gaey to unmein se sirf aik aurat ne addhey insan ko janm diya. kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar wo inshaAllah keh letey to qism zaroor poori hoti aur ye ( qism ( unke dil ki zaroorat poori honey ka zaria bhi bin jati."
4289,"Warqa ne abu-Zanad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : Hazrat Sulaimaan-bin-Daawood (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : aaj raat main nawwey aurton ke paas jaaunga unmein se har aurat aik shehsawar bachchey ko janm degi jo (bada ho kar) Allah ki raah mein ladai karega. to unke sathi ne unse kaha : inshaAllah kahein. unhon-ne inshaAllah na kaha, wo un sab ke paas gaey to unmein se aik aurat ke siwa koi haamla na hui aur us ne bhi aadhey bachchey ko janm diya. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! agar wo inshaAllah keh detey to wo sab ghodon par Sawar ho kar Allah ki raah mein jihad kartey."
4290,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne abu-Zanad se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne kaha : unmein se har aik ke hamal mein aisa bachcha hota jo Allah Taala ki raah mein jihad karta."
4291,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ye hadisen hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne chand hadisein bayan kin, unmein se ye thi : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! tum mein se kisi ka apne ghar walon ke barey main apni qism par israar karna uske liye Allah ke yahan us se zyada gunah ka baais hai ke wo is qism ke liye Allah ka muqarrar karda kaffara de. (aur usey tod kar durust kaam karey aur ghar walon ko aaraam pahunchaaey.)"
4292,"Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan ne hamein Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! maine jahiliyat mein nazar maana thi ke main aik raat masjide-haram mein aetikaf karunga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apni nazar poori karo."
4293,"abu-Usama, abdul-Wahab Saqafi, Hafs bin Ghiyas aur Shoba, un sab ne Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unmein se Hafs ne kaha : (ye hadis) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi hai, abu-Usama aur Saqafi ki hadis mein aik raat aetikaf karne ka tazkira hai aur Shoba ki hadis mein hai ke unhon-ne kaha : din ke aetikaf ki nazar maani. Hafs ki hadis mein din ya raat ka zikr nahi hai."
4294,"Jareer-bin-Haazim ne hamein hadis sunai ke Ayub ne unhein hadis bayan ki, unhein Naafe ne hadis sunai, unhein Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya, aap us waqt Taaif se lotney ke baad Jaarana main (thahrey huey) they, unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! maine jahiliyat mein nazar maana thi ke main aik din masjide-haram mein aetikaf karunga, aap ki kya raey hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jao aur aik din ka aetikaf karo. kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein khums se aik londi ata farmai thi, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ke qaidiyon ko aazad kya, to Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne unki aawaazein sunin, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein aazad kar diya hai. to unhon-ne puchha : kya maajraa hai? logon ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ke qaidiyon ko aazad kar diya hai, to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne (apne betey se) kaha : Abdullah! us londi ke paas jao aur usey aazad kar do. (ye Hunain ka mauqa tha. ("
4295,"Mamar ne hamein Ayub se khabar di, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hunain se wapas huey to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik din ke aetikaf ki nazar ke mutaalliq puchha jo unhon-ne jahiliyat mein maana thi. padhi. phir Jareer-bin-Haazim ki hadis ke ham mana bayan kya."
4296,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ayub ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas Jaarana se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Umerey ka tazkira kya gaya to unhon-ne kaha : aap ne wahan se Umra nahi kya. kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne jahiliyat mein aik raat ke aetikaf ki nazar maana thi. padhi. phir unhon-ne Ayub se Jareer-bin-Haazim aur Mamar ki riwayat ki hui hadis ke ham mana bayan kya."
4297,Ayub aur Muhammad-bin Ishaq donon ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se nazar ke barey mein yahi hadis bayan ki aur un donon ki hadis mein aik din ke aetikaf ka zikr hai.
4298,"Abu-Awana ne faraas se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh Zakwan se aur unhon-ne abu umr azan se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan aaya jabke unhon-ne aik ghulam ko aazad kya tha. kaha : unhon-ne zamin se lakdi ya koi cheez pakdi aur kaha : usmein itna bhi ajr nahi jo iske barabar ho iske siwa ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jisne apne ghulam ko thappad maara ya usey zad w koob kya to uska kaffara ye hai ke usey aazad karey (is hukm ko manney ka ajr ho sakta hai.)"
4299,"Shoba ne hamein faraas se baqi bachi pichhli sanad se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne ghulam ko bulaya aur uski pusht par) zarb ka ( nishan dekha to us se kaha : maine tumhen dukh diya hai? usne kaha : nahi. unhon-ne kaha : tum aazad ho. kaha : phir unhon-ne zamin se koi cheez pakdi aur kaha : mere liye usmein itna bhi ajr nahi hai jo iske barabar ho. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha, aap farma rahe they : jisne apne ghulam ko had lagaaney ke liye ( aisey kaam par) maara jo usney nahi kya ya usey tamaancha maara to uska kaffara ye hai ke usey aazad kar de."
4300,"Wakee aur Abdur-Rehman (bin Mehdi ( donon ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne faraas se Shoba aur abu-Awana ki sanad ke sath riwayat ki, ibne- Mehdi ne apni hadis mein had ka zikr kya hai aur Wakee ki hadis mein hai : jisne apne ghulam ko tamaancha maara . unhon-ne had ka zikr nahi kya."
4301,"Muawiya bin Suwed (bin Muqrin) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine apne aik ghulam ko tamaancha maara aur bhag gaya, phir main Zohar se thodi der pahley aaya aur apne walid ke peechhey Namaz padhi, unhon-ne usey aur mujhey bulaya , phir ( ghulam se) kaha is se pura badla ley lo to usne maaf kar diya. phir unhon ( mere walid ( ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein ham bani Muqrin ke paas sirf aik khaadima thi, ham mein se kisi ne usey tamaancha mar diya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye baat pahunchi to aap ne farmaya : usey aazad kar do. logon ne kaha : unke paas iske ilawa aur khaadim nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo (filhal) us se khidmat lein, jab us se be-niyaaz ho jayen (doosra intizam ho jaey) to uska rasta chhod dein (usey aazad kar dein.)"
4302,"ibne-Idrees ne hamein Husain se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hilal-bin-Yasaf se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik boodhey ne jaldi ki aur apne khaadim ko tamaancha de maara, to Hazrat Suwed bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : tumhen iske sharif chehrey ke siwa aur koi jagah na mili? maine apne aapko Muqrin ke beton mein se saatwan beta paya, hamarey paas sirf aik khaadima thi, ham mein se sabse chhotey ne usey tamaancha maara to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein usko aazad kar dene ka hukm diya."
4303,"Hilal bin Yasaf se riwayat hai ham kapda bechtey they Suwed bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein jo Nauman bin Muqrin ‌ (Raziallahu anhu) ke bhai they, aik londi wahan nikli aur us ne ham main se kisi ko koi baat kahi to usne londi ko tamaancha maara. Suwed ‌(Raziallahu anhu) naraz huey phir bayan kya isi tarah jaisey uper guzra."
4304,"Abdus-Samad ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujh se Muhammad-bin-Munkadir ne kaha : tumhara naam kya hai? maine kaha : Shoba. to Muhammad ne kaha : mujhey abu Shoba Iraaqi (Maula Suwed bin Muqrin) ne Suwed bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke unki londi ko kisi insan ne thappad maara to Suwed (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : kya tumhen malum nahi ke chehra hurmat wala ( hota ( hai aur kaha : maine khud ko , aur main apne bhaiyon mein saatwan tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath dekha aur hamarey paas siwaey aik ke koi aur khaadim na tha. ham mein se kisi ne jaan-boojhkar usey tamaancha mar diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke ham usey aazad kar dein."
4305,Wahab bin Jarir ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne khabar di ke Muhammad-bin Munkadir ne mujh se puchha : tumhara naam kya hai? aagey Abdus-Samad ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya.
4306,"abdul-Wahid bin Ziyad ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash ne Ibrahim Taimi se hadis sunaai, unhon-ne apne walid (Yazeed-bin Sharik Taimi) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat abu Masood badri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main apne aik ghulam ko kode se mar raha tha to maine apne peechhey se awaaz suni : abu Masood! jaan lo. main ghussey ki wjah se awaz na pehchan saka, kaha : jab wo (kehney waale) mere qareeb pahunchey to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) they, aap farma rahe they : Abu-Masood! jaan lo, abu Masood! jaan lo. kaha : maine apne hath se kodaa phenk diya, to aap ne farmaya : abu Masood ! jaan lo. us ghulam par tumhen jitna ikhtiyar hai uski nisbat Allah tum par zyada ikhtiyar rakhta hai. kaha : to maine kaha : iske baad main kisi ghulam ko kabhi nahi maaroonga."
4307,"Jareer, Sufiyan aur abu-Awana sab ne Aamash se abdul-Wahid ki (pichhli) sanad ke sath uski hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, magar Jarir ki hadis mein hai : aap ki haibat ki wjah se mere hath se koda gir gaya."
4308,"abu-Muawia ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash ne Ibrahim Taimi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main apne ghulam ko mar raha tha to maine apne peechhey se awaz suni : Abu-Masood! jaan lo, is par tumhara jitna ikhtiyar hai, uski nisbat Allah tum par zyada ikhtiyar rakhta hai. main muda to dekha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) they, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! wo Allah ki raza ke liye aazad hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dekho ! agar tum aisa na kartey to tumhen aag jhulsaati ya tumhen aag chhooti."
4309,"ibne-abi Adi ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Sulaiman se, unhon-ne Ibrahim Taimi se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo apne ghulam ko mar rahe they, to usne اعوذباللہ (main tumhari mar se Allah ki panah mein aata hun) kehna shuru kar diya. kaha : to (wo uski baat ki taraf mutwajjeh na ho paaey aur) usey maartey rahe. phir usne kaha : main Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki panah mein aata hun to (unhein andaza hua ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif ley aaey hain) unhon-ne usey chhod diya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qasam! Allah tum par us se zyada ikhtiyar rakhta hai jitna tum is par rakhtey ho. kaha : to unhon-ne usey aazad kar diya."
4310,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein Shoba se, isi sanad ke sath khabar di aur unhon-ne ye alfaz bayan nahi kiye : main Allah ki panah mein aata hun (aur) Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki panah mein aata hun."
4311,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Fuzel bin Ghazawan ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdur-Rehman bin abi-Nu-am se suna (kaha :) mujhey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : abul-Qasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne apne ghulam par zina ki tohmat lagai usey qiyamat ke din had lagai jaeygi, siwaey-iske ke wo ( ghulam ( waisaa ho jaisa usne kaha hai."
4312,Wakee aur Ishaq-bin-Yoosuf Azraq donon ne Fuzail-bin-Ghazawan se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur un donon ki hadis mein hai : maine abul-Qaasim Nabi Tauba (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna.
4313,"Wakee ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Maroor-bin-Suwed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rabza (ke maqam ( mein Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan se guzrey, un (ke jism) par aik chadar thi aur unke ghulam (ke jism ( par bhi waisi hi chadar thi. to ham ne kaha : Abu-Zar ! agar aap un donon (chaadaron) ko ikattha kar letey to ye aik hulla bin jata. unhon-ne kaha : mere aur mere kisi ( musalman ( bhai ke darmyan talkh kalami hui, uski maan ajami thi, maine usey uski maa ke hawale se aar dilai to usne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas meri shikayat kar di, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mila to aap ne farmaya : Abu-Zar ! tum aisey aadmi ho ke tum mein jahiliyat (ki aadat maujood ( hai. maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! jo dusron ko bura bhala kehta hai wo iske maan aur bap ko bura bhala kehtey hain. aap ne farmaya : Abu-Zar ! tum aisey aadmi ho jis mein jahiliyat hai, wo ( chahey kaneez zadey hon ya ghulam ya ghulam zadey ( tumharey bhai hain, Allah ne unhein tumharey ma-tehet kya hai, tum unhein wahi khilaao jo khud khaatey ho aur wahi pahnaao jo khud pahntey ho aur un par aisey kaam ki zimme-dari na dalo jo unke bas se bahar ho, agar un par (mushkil kaam ki) zimme-dari dalo to unki iaanat karo."
4314,"Zuhair, abu-Muawia aur Esa-bin-Yonus sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, Zuhair aur abu-Muawiya ki hadis mein aap ke farman : tum aisey aadmi ho jis mein jahiliyat hai ke baad ye izafa hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine kaha : budhapey ki us ghadi ke bawajud bhi) jahiliyat ki aadat baqi hai? (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan. abu-Muawiya ki riwayat mein hai : haan , tumharey budhapey ki us ghadi ke bawajud bhi Esa ki hadis mein hai : agar wo is par aisi zimme-dari daal de jo uski taqat se bahar hai to (behtar hai) usey bech de. (ghulam par zulm ke gunah se bach jaey.) Zuhair ki hadis mein hai : to wo us ( kaam ( mein uski iaanat kare. abu-Muawiya ki hadis mein wo usey bech de aur wo uski iaanat karey ke alfaz nahi hain aur unki hadis aap ke farman : is par aisi zimme-dari na daley jo iske bas se bahar ho. par khatm ho gaee."
4315,"Wasil ahadab ne Maroor-bin-Suwed se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko us haalat mein dekha ke un (ke jism ( par) aadha ( hulla tha aur unke ghulam par bhi isi tarah ka ( aadha ( hulla tha, maine unse iske barey mein poochha, kaha : to unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein unhon-ne aik aadmi ko bura-bhala kaha aur usey uski maan (ke ajamii honey) ki (bina par) aar dilai, kaha : to wo aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aapko ye baat batai , is par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum aisey aadmi ho jis mein jahiliyat (ki khoo ( hai, wo tumharey bhai aur khidmat guzaar hain, Allah ne unhein tumharey ma-tehet kya hai, to jiska bhai iske ma-tehet ho wo usey usi khaney mein se khilaey jo wo khud khata hai aur wahi libas pehnaey jo khud pehnta hai aur unke zimmey aisa kaam na lagaao jo unke bas se bahar ho aur agar tum unke zimmey lagaao to is par unki madad karo."
4316,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : khana aur libaas ghulam ka haq hai aur is par kaam ki itni zimme-dari na dali jaey jo iske bas mein na ho."
4317,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ka khaadim uske liye khana taiyaar karey, phir iske samney pesh karey aur usi ne ( aag ki) tapish aur dhuan bardasht kya hai to wo usey apne sath bithaaey aur wo (ghulam bhi uske saath) khaaey aur agar khana bahut se logon ne khana liya ho, (yani ( kam ho to uske hath mein aik ya 2 luqmey (zaroor) de."
4318,Imam Malik ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ghulam jab apne aaqa ki khairkhaahi karey aur achi tarah Allah ki bandagi karey to uske liye dohra ajr hai.
4319,"Ubaidullah aur Usama ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Imam Malik ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4320,"abu-Taahir aur Hurmala bin Yahya ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se suna, wo keh rahe they, Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : achi tarah zimme daariyaan nibhaaney waley kisi ke mamlook (ghulam) ke liye 2 ajr hain. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Abu-Hurera ki jaan hai! agar Allah ki raah mein jihad, Haj aur apni walida ki khidmat ( jaisey kaam ( na hotey to main pasand karta ke main marun to ghulam hun. (Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne) kaha : hamein ye baat pahunchi hai ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) apni walida ki wafat tak unke sath rehney (aur khidmat karne) ki bina par Haj nahi kartey they. abu-Taahir ne apni hadis main achi tarah zimme daariyaan nibhaaney wala ( عَبد ( ) ghulam ( kaha, mamlook nahi kaha."
4321,"abu-Safwaan umwii ne hamein hadis bayan ki (kaha : ( mujhey Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath khabar di, unhon-ne 'hamein ye baat pahunchi' aur uske baad wala hissey bayan nahi kya."
4322,"Abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab ghulam Allah ka haq aur apne malikon ka haq ada karey to uske liye 2 ajr hain. kaha : maine ye hadis Kab ko sunai to Kab ne kaha : na us ( ghulam (ka hisab hoga na hi kam maal waley momin ka hisab hoga."
4323,Jarir ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
4324,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin, unmein se ye bhi thi : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi ghulam ka is haal mein faut ho jana kya khub hai ke wo Allah ki bandagi aur apne aaqa ki khidmat achchhey tareeqey se kar raha tha! uske liye kya khub hai ye ( zindagi ! ("
4325,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne kisi ( mushtarka ( ghulam (ki milkiyat mein) se apna hissey aazad kya aur uske paas itna maal hai jo ghulam ki qeemat ko pahunchta hai to uski munsifaana qeemat lagai jaeygi aur uske sharikon ko unke hissey diye jaeinge aur ghulam uski taraf se aazad ho jaeyga warna wo itna hi aazad rahega jitna pahley ho gaya hai."
4326,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne kisi ghulam (ki milkiyat mein) se apna hissey aazad kya, agar uske paas itna maal hai jo uski qeemat ko pahunchta hai to uski poori aazaadi us par) lazim ( hai. aur agar uske paas maal nahi hai to wo jitna aazad ho chuka tha itna hi aazad rahega."
4327,"Jareer-bin-Hazim ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne kisi ( mushtarka ( ghulam (ki milkiyat mein) se apna hissey aazad kya aur uske paas itni miqdar mein maal hai jo uski qeemat ko pahunchta hai, to uski munsifaana qeemat lagai jaeygi (aur Sharik ko uska hissey ada karke ghulam uski taraf se aazad kya jaeyga) warna wo jitna aazad ho chuka tha itna hi aazad rahega."
4328,"Lais-bin-Sad , Yahya-bin-Saeed , Ayub , Ismail bin Umayya , ibne-abi-Ze-ib aur Usama-bin-Zaid sab ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis bayan ki, Ayub aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ki hadis ke siwa unmein se kisi ki hadis mein ye alfaz nahi hain : aur agar uske paas maal nahi to wo jitna aazad ho chuka tha itna hi aazad rahega aur unhi donon ne ye jumla kaha aur un donon ( Ayub aur Yahya ( ne ye bhi kaha : hamein malum nahi hai ke ye hadis ka hissa hai ya Naafe ne apni taraf se kaha hai. aur Lais-bin-Sad ki hadis ke siwa unmein se kisi ki riwayat mein ""maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna"" ke alfaz nahi hain."
4329,"Amr ne Salim bin-Abdullah se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne apne aur kisi doosrey ke darmyan mushtarak ghulam ko aazad kya to kami beshi ke baghair uske maal mein se ( ghulam ki) munsifaana qeemat lagai jaeygi, phir agar wo khush haal hua to wo iske maal se uski taraf se aazad ho jaeyga"
4330,"Zohri ne Salim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne kisi ghulam (ki milkiyat mein) se apna hissey aazad kya to uska baqi hissey bhi uske maal se aazad hoga, basharte ke uske paas itna maal ho jo ghulam ki qeemat ko pahunch jaey."
4331,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne nazar bin Anas se, unhon-ne Bashir bin-Nuhaik se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne 2 aadmiyon ke mushtarka ghulam ke barey mein jin mein se aik (apna hissa) aazad kar deta hai, farmaya : wo (doosrey ka ( zaamin hai. (ke iske hissey ki qeemat usey mil jaeygi.)"
4332,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, aap ne farmaya : jisne ghulam (ki milkiyat) mein se apna hissey aazad kya to wo usi ke maal se ( pura ( aazad ho jaeyga."
4333,"Ismail bin Ibrahim ne ibne-abi-Aruba se, unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne nazar bin Anas se, unhon-ne Bashir bin Nuhaik se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jisne ghulam (ki milkiyat ( mein se apna hissey aazad kya, agar uske paas maal hai to uski ( poori ( aazadi usi ke maal ke zariey se hogi aur agar uske paas maal nahi hai to kisi jabrii mashaqqat mein daley baghair us ghulam se ( Baqiya qeemat ki adaaeygi ke liye) kaam karwaya jaeyga."
4334,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir, Muhammad-bin-Bishr aur Esa-bin-Yonus sab ne ibne-abi-Aruba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur Esa ki hadis mein hai : usey kisi mashaqqat mein daley baghair, us shakhs ke hissey (ki adaaeygi) ke liye kaam liya jaeyga jisne aazad nahi kya."
4335,"Ismail-bin-Ulaih ne Ayub se, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se, unhon-ne abu-Mohlab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne apni maut ke waqt apne chh ghulam aazad kiye aur uske paas unke siwa aur koi maal na tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bulwaya aur teen grupon mein taqseem kya, phir unke darmyan Qura daala, iske baad 2 ko aazad kar diya aur char ko ghulam hi bar-qaraar rakha aur aap ne usey sarzanish ki."
4336,"Hammad aur (abdul-Wahab) Saqafi donon ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, Hammad ki hadis ibne-Uleh ki hadis ki tarah hai aur Saqafi ki hadis mein hai : Ansar ke aik aadmi ne apni maut ke waqt wasiyat ki aur chh ghulam aazad kar diye."
4337,"Yazeed bin Zaree ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hisham bin Hassan ne Muhammad-bin Sirin se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ibne-Ulaih aur Hammad ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
4338,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Ansar mein se aik aadmi ne apni maut ke baad apne ghulam ko aazad qarar diya, uske paas iske siwa aur koi maal na tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye baat pahunchi to aap ne farmaya is (ghulam) ko mujh se kon khareedega? usey Naeem bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne aath so dirham mein khareed liya to aap ne wo (raqam) us aadmi ke hawale kar di. Amr ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : wo qibtii ghulam tha ( ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ki amaarat ke) pahley saal faut hua. (apni maut ke baad ghulam ko aazad karne waley ko aik tehai se zyada tarkey mein wasiiyat ka ikhtiyar hi na tha.)"
4339,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha : Amr (bin Dinar) ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Ansar ke aik aadmi ne apni maut ke baad apne ghulam ke aazad honey ki wasiiyat ki, kaha : uske paas iske ilawa aur koi maal na tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey farokht kar diya, Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : usey ibne-Naham ne khareeda, wo qibti ghulam tha, Hazrat ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ki amaarat ke pahley saal faut hua."
4340,"Lais-bin-Sad ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mudabbir (Malik ki maut ke baad aazad hone-waale ghulam) ke barey mein Amr-bin-Dinar se riwayat ki hui Hammad ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki."
4341,"Abdul-Majeed bin Suhel aur Husain bin Zakwan muallim ne Ata se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, isi tarah Matar bin Tehmaan al-Warraq ne Ata-bin-abi-Ribah, abu-Zubair aur Amr-bin-Dinar se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein mudabbir ke saudey ke barey mein hadis bayan ki, un sab (Ata, abu-Zubair aur Amr ( ne kaha : unhon ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki jo Hammad aur ibne-Uena ne Amr se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan ki."
